  "title": "Statutory Financials Demystified",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"ContentPanel\" id=\"mainContentWrapper\">\n<div data-height-offset=\"true\" id=\"masterMainBreadcrumb\"></div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_UserMessagesUpdatePanel\">\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_PublishUpdatePanel\">\n</div><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1___Drag\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;z-index:32000;filter:alpha(opacity=75);\">\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone1_Page1\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage1$HiddenDownloadPathField\" type=\"hidden\"/><input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_downloadButton\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage1$downloadButton\" style=\"display:none\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Download Path\"/>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone2_Page1\">\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_Panel_NewContentHtml\">\n<h2>Statutory Financials Demystified</h2>\n<div>The insights brief below captures key insights from our live webinar, Statutory Financials Demystified: What Insurance Leaders Need to Know, held on September 16, 2025. Hosted by Andrew Chmil, CPA, Group Controller at Tower Hill Insurance Group, the session explored statutory reporting, SAP vs. GAAP, and how to apply financial insights to leadership decision-making.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<p><a class=\"btn TextButton PrimaryButton\" href=\"/common/Uploaded%20files/Insights/Statutory%20Financials%20Demystified%20Webinar%20Summary.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download Summary</a></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml3_86d1038f739f4854a0efb4b41b617cfd\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml3_86d1038f739f4854a0efb4b41b617cfd_ciNewContentHtml3_86d1038f739f4854a0efb4b41b617cfd_Panel_NewContentHtml3\">\n<div style=\"margin:0px auto; position:relative; height:0; overflow:hidden; max-width:904px; padding-bottom:2714px;\"></div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage2$HiddenDownloadPathField\" type=\"hidden\"/><input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_downloadButton\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage2$downloadButton\" style=\"display:none\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Download Path\"/>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone3_Page1\">\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667_ciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667_Panel_NewContentHtml2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/common/Uploaded%20files/Insights/Statutory%20Financials%20Demystified%20Webinar%20Summary.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/IASA/Insight%20Articles/9-16-25-Webinar-StatFin-download1.png?version=A4E36BA9\"/></a><br/></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage3_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage3_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage3$HiddenDownloadPathField\"